steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "REST" API
I pass a "format = xls and query = cancer and offset = 0 and hits = 10 and expectedValues = exportTrialResults_Smoke_2_1.xls" as parameter to "exportCompanyResultsV2" operation
check the requested file is found in the following path "exportTrialResults_Smoke_2_1.xls"

check for all the columns "Company Name,Parent Company Name,Country/Territory,Key Indications,Key Target-based Actions,Key Technologies,Number of Drugs in Active Development,Number of Inactive Drugs,Number of Deals,Number of Patents as Owner,Number of Patents as Third Party" in the file
I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API
I pass a "format = MS_EXCEL and query = cancer and offset = 0 and hits = 10 and expectedValues = exportTrialResults_Smoke_2_1.xls" as parameter to "exportCompanyResultsV2" operation
check the requested file is found in the following path "exportTrialResults_Smoke_2_1.xls"

check for all the columns "Company Name,Parent Company Name,Country/Territory,Key Indications,Key Target-based Actions,Key Technologies,Number of Drugs in Active Development,Number of Inactive Drugs,Number of Deals,Number of Patents as Owner,Number of Patents as Third Party" in the file
